    <note>Chen(1) Cisheng [11080] Apt. investigating censor in ca. 1095 and impeached both Zhang(2) Dun and Cai(1) Bian. Purged by Bian. In 1101, he was appointed Executive censor and impeached Zhang(2) Dun, Cai(1) Bian, Zeng(1) Bu and Cai(1) Jing. Purged by Cai Jing in 1102 and entered as a member of the Yuanfu coalition. Partially rehabilitated during 1111-1117 period. Biographical sources include lots of coalitional information. Check. YLDD, 3146.3b-11a. CBD, 3, 2563.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:1095:  (ca.) Apt. investigating censor (yushi).1101:  (ca.) appointed executive censor.1102:  purged.</note>
